                    <img class="media-object small-arrow" alt="64x64" src="~/Content/images/Qiran vertical.png" />

                </a>
                <div class="media-body">
                    <ul style="position:relative">
                        <li>
                            Wear Ihram attire. For men just two sheets of unsown white cloth and women can wear any clothing as long as it conforms to the Islamic code of dress.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="media" style="position:relative">
                <a href="#" class="pull-left">
                    <span class="stepPosition3">
                        <span class="badge">3</span>

                        <br />
                       2 rakat salah <br />before making <br />
